    <h2>System Information</h2>
        <p>
        	Functions in this section are used to obtain different data. System configuration information 
        	describes the computer hardware, computer name and user name. Operating system information 
        	describes the operating system version, key directories, and environment variables etc. System 
        	parameters describes the system properties. System guidelines provide the size of display area 
        	elements.
        </p>

